---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="关于" description="了解更多关于健身为王项目的信息">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">关于</h1>
    
    <div class="fitness-card p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">健身为王</h2>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        健身为王是一个开源的个人健身追踪平台，帮助你记录训练，管理计划，坚持锻炼。
      </p>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">功能特性</h3>
      
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>每日训练</strong> - 随机生成每日训练，坚持打卡</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>训练库</strong> - 预置多种分类训练，随时选择</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>月度挑战</strong> - 参与挑战，培养锻炼习惯</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>健身计划</strong> - 创建个性化训练计划</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>用户系统</strong> - 云端保存数据，多设备同步</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>响应式设计</strong> - 完美适配手机和桌面</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mr-2">✓</span>
          <span><strong>深色模式</strong> - 支持浅色/深色主题切换</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">技术架构</h3>
      
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
        <li><strong>前端:</strong> Astro + TailwindCSS，静态站点，GitHub Pages 托管</li>
        <li><strong>后端:</strong> Node.js + Express + SQLite + JWT 认证</li>
        <li><strong>部署:</strong> 前后端分离，前端免费托管 GitHub，后端部署自己服务器</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 mt-6 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">开始使用</h3>
      
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        点击右上角登录/注册，开始你的健身之旅吧！坚持就是胜利！💪
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <p>Made with 💪 for fitness lovers</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
